high_descs: Turn around, go to end of table on right.  Turn right to face table.
Pick up knife from table, located behind the wine bottle and in front of the right green sponge.
Turn around and go to sink.
Place knife to left of egg in sink, turn water on, turn water off, drain water.  Pick up knife.
Place knife on table, directly in front of the spoon to the right of the pencil.
anns.task_desc: Wash knife and return to table.

high_descs: Turn around, walk to end of kitchen island
Pick up knife behind wine bottle on kitchen island
Place knife in sink, turn on water, turn off water, pick up knife
Turn around, walk to kitchen island
anns.task_desc: Pick up knife, clean it, return knife

high_descs: Turn around and go forward and turn to the right to face the green table.
Pick the large knife up from the table.
Turn around and face the sink.
Put the knife in the sink and turn the water on and then off and pick the knife up again.
Turn around and face the green table again.
Put the knife on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean knife on a table.
